{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"fbdb26dd-f2da-4b58-a304-eb42a335d0cf","content":"The directory is empty, so this is a general guidance question. Here's how to migrate:\n\n### Replace `VSTest@3` with `DotNetCoreCLI@2` (or a script)\n\nMicrosoft.Testing.Platform doesn't use `vstest.console.exe`, so `VSTest@3` won't work. Use `dotnet test` instead:\n\n```yaml\n# Before (VSTest runner)\n- task: VSTest@3\n  inputs:\n    testAssemblies: '**/*Tests.dll'\n    codeCoverageEnabled: true\n\n# After (Microsoft.Testing.Platform)\n- task: DotNetCoreCLI@2\n  displayName: 'Run tests'\n  inputs:\n    command: test\n    projects: '**/*Tests.csproj'\n    arguments: >-\n      --configuration Release\n      --logger \"trx;LogFileName=TestResults.trx\"\n      --results-directory $(Agent.TempDirectory)/TestResults\n      --collect \"Code Coverage\"\n```\n\n### Key changes\n\n1. **TRX reports** — pass `--logger trx` to `dotnet test`; the platform still emits `.trx` files.\n2. **Code coverage** — use `--collect \"Code Coverage\"` (or switch to Coverlet with `--collect:\"XPlat Code Coverage\"`).\n3. **Publish results** — add a separate step if you're not using `DotNetCoreCLI@2` (which auto-publishes):\n\n```yaml\n- task: PublishTestResults@2\n  condition: always()\n  inputs:\n    testResultsFormat: VSTest\n    testResultsFiles: '$(Agent.TempDirectory)/TestResults/**/*.trx'\n\n- task: PublishCodeCoverageResults@2\n  inputs:\n    summaryFileLocation: '$(Agent.TempDirectory)/TestResults/**/*.cobertura.xml'\n```\n\n4. **Project setup** — ensure each test project opts in:\n\n```xml\n<PropertyGroup>\n  <EnableMSTestRunner>true</EnableMSTestRunner>\n  <OutputType>Exe</OutputType>\n</PropertyGroup>\n```\n\n### Why the change matters\n\n`VSTest@3` discovers and runs test **DLLs** via `vstest.console`. With Microsoft.Testing.Platform, each test project is a **self-contained executable** invoked through `dotnet test`, so assembly-glob patterns like `**/*Tests.dll` no longer apply — you reference **projects** instead.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"6e89f83f-e7b4-4f5e-9f19-a5bc8c907734","outputTokens":587,"requestId":"702B:2AE020:D7E3C2E:EE31355:69F2A861"},"id":"46a99c23-5810-45a6-99a9-b139504f81aa","timestamp":"2026-04-30T00:55:09.297Z","parentId":"17e3493b-87bb-4e1c-8219-d56c0f563149"}
